parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The deterioration of the headlight reflector can cause poor visibility and illumination, making it difficult or impossible to drive at night, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: black spots or areas on the reflector
chrome or plastic reflector material degrading or melting
headlight bulbs dimming or failing to illuminate the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rubber Coupler Failure between Carburetor and Intake Manifold
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rubber coupler can cause the engine to sputter and die, leading to a loss of power and control, which can be extremely dangerous, especially at high speeds.
